attachments.fallback: [January 13th, 2021 5:29 PM] hector.merchan: I think the upgrade to DBInterface is producing an error on the execute function. DBInterface.execute statements are producing an error about an ambiguity with ODBC.execute. Downgrading to Do interface v2.2.0 fixes the error.
